  objectiveLabels:
  - Result acceptance, comeback record, disclosures aur deadlines audit karein
  - First-election gaps, corrections aur measurable lessons publish karein
  - Targets, costs, funding sources aur review dates wala manifesto verify karein
  - Regional autonomy, dissent, cabinet aur exit rules ka contract sign karein
  - Local-language, easy-read, captioned aur accessible media approve karein
  - Service records, beneficiary privacy aur campaign firewall verify karein
  - Listening coalition ya massive comeback wave mein decision lein
  - Equal-time debate, coalition questions aur correction window complete karein
  - Donations, coalition shares, caps, invoices aur vendors audit karein
  - Accessibility, neutral safety, observers aur result-form operations train karein
  - Corrections, promotion pause, volunteer freeze aur result protocol activate karein
  - Independent fictional 100-seat count aur PM mandate dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 03000000070000000a000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - LESSONS APPLIED
  - CAMPAIGN MODEL LOCKED
  - POLL SYSTEM READY
  milestoneMessages:
  - Eligibility, first-election lessons and updated manifesto verified hain. Coalition
    and accessibility next hain.
  - Coalition contract, accessibility, service firewall and campaign strategy ready
    hain. Debate and finance next hain.
  - Debate, finance and neutral polling operations verified hain. Silence protocol
    independent count unlock karega.
